{"uuid": "e6106d91-07df-475f-9be3-b3046fb03dec", "id": 63394, "date": "2025-12-21T04:00:04", "date_gmt": "2025-12-21T12:00:04", "guid": {"rendered": "https://estreetshuffle.com/?p=63394"}, "modified": "2025-11-18T18:24:39", "modified_gmt": "2025-11-19T02:24:39", "slug": "kingdom-of-days-december-21-2", "status": "publish", "type": "post", "link": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2025/12/21/kingdom-of-days-december-21-2/", "title": {"rendered": "Kingdom of Days: December 21"}, "content": {"rendered": "<p><em><strong>New for 2025:\u00a0</strong>No updates</em></p>\n<p><strong>1973: &#8220;</strong>Bruce Springsteen and his studio band&#8221; headline at Sandy&#8217;s in Beverly, Massachusetts.</p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"14772\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1973-12-21/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/1973-12-21.jpg?fit=373%2C500&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"373,500\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1973-12-21\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/1973-12-21.jpg?fit=224%2C300&amp;ssl=1\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/1973-12-21.jpg?fit=373%2C500&amp;ssl=1\" class=\" wp-image-14772 aligncenter\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/1973-12-21-224x300.jpg?resize=758%2C1015\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"1015\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/1973-12-21.jpg?resize=224%2C300&amp;ssl=1 224w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/1973-12-21.jpg?w=373&amp;ssl=1 373w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>1975:\u00a0</strong>Bruce and the E Street Band bring the Born to Run Tour to Seneca College in Toronto.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" title=\"Bruce Springsteen - 12/21/75 Toronto Live Concert\" width=\"758\" height=\"426\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/olusvTlt3_0?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" referrerpolicy=\"strict-origin-when-cross-origin\" allowfullscreen></iframe></div>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"55377\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2024/12/21/kingdom-of-days-december-21/the_toronto_star_1975_12_22_19/#main\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/The_Toronto_Star_1975_12_22_19.jpg?fit=1291%2C1957&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"1291,1957\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"The_Toronto_Star_1975_12_22_19\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/The_Toronto_Star_1975_12_22_19.jpg?fit=198%2C300&amp;ssl=1\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/The_Toronto_Star_1975_12_22_19.jpg?fit=676%2C1024&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-55377\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/The_Toronto_Star_1975_12_22_19.jpg?resize=758%2C1149&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"1149\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/The_Toronto_Star_1975_12_22_19.jpg?w=1291&amp;ssl=1 1291w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/The_Toronto_Star_1975_12_22_19.jpg?resize=198%2C300&amp;ssl=1 198w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/The_Toronto_Star_1975_12_22_19.jpg?resize=676%2C1024&amp;ssl=1 676w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/The_Toronto_Star_1975_12_22_19.jpg?resize=768%2C1164&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/The_Toronto_Star_1975_12_22_19.jpg?resize=1013%2C1536&amp;ssl=1 1013w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>1985:\u00a0</strong><em>Born in the U.S.A.</em> passes Michael Jackson&#8217;s <em>Thriller</em> to take the #2 spot for longest-run on the Billboard Top 10. Lasting for an amazing 79 weeks, it still won&#8217;t come close to the number one champion: the soundtrack to <em>The Sound of Music</em>.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" title=\"Born In The U.S.A.\" width=\"758\" height=\"426\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/videoseries?list=OLAK5uy_knulz6rBDTjgdDwskLxzD8g7gAdqRY4T0\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" referrerpolicy=\"strict-origin-when-cross-origin\" allowfullscreen></iframe></div>\n<p><strong>1998:\u00a0</strong>Bruce holds his annual Christmas party at McLoone&#8217;s Rum Runner in Sea Bright, where he joins Bobby Bandiera&#8217;s band for &#8220;<a href=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2021/12/24/cover-me-santa-claus-is-comin-to-town/\">Santa Claus is Comin&#8217; to Town.</a>&#8221;</p>\n<p><strong>2017:\u00a0</strong><em>Springsteen on Broadway\u00a0</em>continues its theatrical run at the Walter Kerr Theater in New York City.</p>\n<p><strong>2020:\u00a0</strong>Bruce performs a gorgeous acoustic version of &#8220;<a href=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2021/01/05/roll-of-the-dice-letter-to-you/\">Letter to You</a>&#8221; (its first live performance, albeit virtual) as part of the\u00a0<em>Stand With Teachers</em> virtual fundraising event.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" title=\"Bruce Springsteen - Letter to You - Springsteen Residence, Colts Neck, NJ (12/21/2020)\" width=\"758\" height=\"426\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/tlHBa5IpCmw?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" referrerpolicy=\"strict-origin-when-cross-origin\" allowfullscreen></iframe></div>\n", "protected": false}, "excerpt": {"rendered": "<p>On this date: Born in the U.S.A. passes Thriller&#8217;s run on the U.S. album chart, Bruce plays his first-ever show in Toronto, and more.</p>\n", "protected": false}, "author": 1, "featured_media": 31606, "comment_status": "open", "ping_status": "open", "sticky": false, "template": "", "format": "standard", "meta": {"_monsterinsights_skip_tracking": false, "_monsterinsights_sitenote_active": false, "_monsterinsights_sitenote_note": "", "_monsterinsights_sitenote_category": 0, "jetpack_post_was_ever_published": false, "_jetpack_newsletter_access": "", "_jetpack_dont_email_post_to_subs": false, "_jetpack_newsletter_tier_id": 0, "_jetpack_memberships_contains_paywalled_content": false, "_jetpack_memberships_contains_paid_content": false, "footnotes": "", "jetpack_publicize_message": "", "jetpack_publicize_feature_enabled": true, "jetpack_social_post_already_shared": true, "jetpack_social_options": {"image_generator_settings": {"template": "highway", "defaul